# Waiter Dashboard Verification Checklist

- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:8080/dashboard/waiter.html
- [ ] Take a screenshot of the waiter cards
- [ ] Inspect `.waiter-table-block` computed background-color
- [ ] Inspect `.waiter-table-number` computed font-size
- [ ] Check if items have bullet points
- [ ] Report findings regarding visual prominence of table numbers
